                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Venez à moi, claquepatins,\nLoqueteux, joueurs de musettes,\nClampins, loupeurs, voyous, catins,\nEt marmousets, et marmousettes,\nTas de traîne-cul-les-housettes,\nRace d’indépendants fougueux !\nJe suis du pays dont vous êtes :\nLe poète est le Roi des Gueux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Vous que la bise des matins,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Que la pluie aux âpres sagettes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Que les gendarmes, les mâtins,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Les coups, les fièvres, les disettes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Prennent toujours pour amusettes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Vous dont l’habit mince et fongueux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Paraît fait de vieilles gazettes.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Le poète est le Roi des Gueux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Vous que la bise des matins,\nQue la pluie aux âpres sagettes,\nQue les gendarmes, les mâtins,\nLes coups, les fièvres, les disettes\nPrennent toujours pour amusettes,\nVous dont l’habit mince et fongueux\nParaît fait de vieilles gazettes.\nLe poète est le Roi des Gueux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Vous que le chaud soleil a teints,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Hurlubiers dont les peaux bisettes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Ressemblent à l’or des gratins,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Gouges au front plein de frisettes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Momignards nus sans chemisettes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Vieux à l’œil cave, au nez rugueux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Au menton en casse-noisettes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Le poète est le Roi des Gueux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Vous que le chaud soleil a teints,\nHurlubiers dont les peaux bisettes\nRessemblent à l’or des gratins,\nGouges au front plein de frisettes,\nMomignards nus sans chemisettes,\nVieux à l’œil cave, au nez rugueux,\nAu menton en casse-noisettes,\nLe poète est le Roi des Gueux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Ô Gueux, mes sujets, mes sujettes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
